      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a beautiful shine, though upon close inspection, you will notice some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound and drives smoothly, making it a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that has been treated with care.",
