      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This well-maintained beauty is in great shape and ready to hit the road! It\u2019s been cared for nicely, offering a smooth drive and a clean look that really stands out. If you're looking for a reliable, high-quality vehicle that\u2019s ready to go from day one, this is the one for you!",
