    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for driver. The exterior showcases a vibrant finish with only minor, age-appropriate imperfections that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and remarkably clean; the upholstery is supple, and every button, switch, and gauge functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, benefiting from a strict schedule of synthetic oil changes and a recent cooling system refresh. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. Included with the sale is a folder of service receipts and a clean title. This car has been a dependable companion and is ready for its next chapter with no immediate work required.",
